source.name: Accident/Incident Overview - Accident Incident Overview
source.description: FRA has made its current and archival Railroad Accident/Incident and Highway Rail Crossing Inventory database files available to all users. Overview data cover current railroad safety statistics on railroad accidents and incidents, casualties.
